在[[幾何學|幾何學]]中，'''立方半八面體'''是一種{{link-en|非凸多面體|Nonconvex polyhedron}}，屬於[[星形多面體|星形多面體]]及[[均勻多面體|均勻多面體]]，也可以歸類在非凸均勻多面體，其索引在均勻多面中是U<sub>15</sub><ref>{{cite web | url = https://archive.lib.msu.edu/crcmath/math/math/c/c835.htm | title = Cubohemioctahedron | publisher = [[密西根州立大學|密西根州立大學]][[圖書館|圖書館]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130620081222/http://archive.lib.msu.edu/crcmath/math/math/c/c835.htm | archivedate = 2013-06-20 | access-date = 2016-08-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[溫尼爾多面體模型列表|溫尼爾多面體模型]]中是W<sub>78</sub><ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160831133741/http://colinspics.org/life/maths/polyhedra/W78%20Cubohemioctahedron.htm | url = http://colinspics.org/life/maths/polyhedra/W78%20Cubohemioctahedron.htm | archivedate = 2016-08-31 | title = W<sub>78</sub> Cubohemioctahedron | publisher = colinspics | access-date = 2016-08-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。立方半八面體外觀看起來像所有[[三角形|三角形]]面都凹進去的[[截半立方體|截半立方體]]。<ref name="wenninger1974polyhedron">{{cite book
  |title=Polyhedron Models
  |author=Wenninger, M.J.
  |isbn=9780521098595
  |lccn=69010200
  |url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=N8lX2T-4njIC
  |year=1974
  |publisher=Cambridge University Press
  |access-date=2021-09-06
  |archive-date=2021-08-31
  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210831094821/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=N8lX2T-4njIC
  |dead-url=no
  }}</ref>{{rp|78}}立方半八面體由6個[[正方形|正方形]]和4個[[正六邊形|正六邊形]]組成，是一種[[十面體|十面體]]，且每個頂點對應的角皆相等，因此也可以被歸類為擬正多面體<ref name="George 1996">{{cite web | url=https://www.georgehart.com/virtual-polyhedra/quasi-regular-index.html | title=Quasi-Regular Polyhedra | author=George W. Hart | year=1996 | access-date=2021-09-05 | archive-date=2021-08-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210830100133/http://www.georgehart.com/virtual-polyhedra/quasi-regular-index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，然而由於這個立體同時具備半多面體的特性，因此被部分學者分成一類新的立體，即擬正半多面體（Versi-Regular Polyhedra），這類立體共有九個，最早在1881年由亞伯特·巴杜羅（{{lang|en|Albert Badoureau}}）發現並描述<ref name="Jean Paul Albert 1881">{{Cite journal|author=Jean Paul Albert Badoureau|title=Mémoire sur les Figures Isocèles|journal=Journal de l'École polytechnique|number=49|year=1881|page=47-172}}</ref>。

== 性質 ==
立方半八面體共有10個[[面_(幾何)|面]]、24條[[邊_(幾何)|邊]]和12個[[頂點_(幾何)|頂點]]<ref name="mathconsult">{{cite web | url = https://www.mathconsult.ch/static/unipoly/15.html | title = Uniform Polyhedra 15: Cubohemioctahedron | publisher = mathconsult | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160327004546/http://www.mathconsult.ch/static/unipoly/15.html | archivedate = 2016-03-27 | access-date = 2016-08-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://bulatov.org/polyhedra/uniform/u20.html | title = Cubohemioctahedron | publisher = bulatov.org | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160401210345/http://bulatov.org/polyhedra/uniform/u20.html | archivedate = 2016-04-01 | access-date = 2016-08-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在其10個面中有6個正方形面和4個六邊形面。這6個正方形面的排列方式與截半立方體的六個正方形面相同<ref name="pisanski2012configurations">{{cite book
  |title=Configurations from a Graphical Viewpoint
  |author=Pisanski, T. and Servatius, B.
  |isbn=9780817683634
  |lccn=2012944998
  |series=Birkhäuser Advanced Texts Basler Lehrbücher
  |url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=3vnEcMCx0HkC
  |year=2012
  |publisher=Birkhäuser Boston
  |access-date=2021-09-06
  |archive-date=2021-09-06
  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210906150239/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=3vnEcMCx0HkC
  |dead-url=no
  }}</ref>{{rp|108}}
。立方半八面體每個頂點都是2個[[正方形|正方形]]和2個六邊形的公共[[頂點_(幾何)|頂點]]。其中，有一個四邊形反向相接，使得其[[頂點圖|頂點圖]]為交叉四邊形，在頂點布局中，可以用4.6.4/3.6來描述。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.software3d.com/CHO.php |title=Cubohemioctahedron |author=Robert Webb |publisher=software3d.com |access-date=2021-09-06 |archive-date=2020-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329052626/https://www.software3d.com/CHO.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="mathconsult"/>

