=== 二面角 ===
八面半八面體[[二面角|二面角]]為[[3的算術平方根|三平方根]]的[[倒數|倒數]]之[[反餘弦|反餘弦]]值<ref>{{cite web | url = http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/Cubohemioctahedron.html | title = Versi-Regular Polyhedra: Cubohemioctahedron | publisher = dmccooey.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324081711/http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/Cubohemioctahedron.html | archivedate = 2016-03-24 | access-date = 2016-08-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>Jean Paul Albert Badoureau, Mémoire sur les Figures Isocèles,
Journal de l'École polytechnique 49 (1881), 47-172.</ref>：
:<math>\cos^{-1} (\frac{\sqrt{3}}{3}) \approx 0.9553166 \approx 54.7356 ^{\circ}</math>

=== 頂點座標 ===
由於立方半八面體[[凸包|凸包]]為[[截半立方體|截半立方體]]，因此其12[[頂點_(幾何)|頂點]]會與[[截半立方體|截半立方體]]相同，為{{nowrap|(0, ±1, ±1)}}、 {{nowrap|(±1, 0, ±1)}}, {{nowrap|(±1, ±1, 0)}}，若邊長為a，則[[座標|座標]]要[[縮放|縮放]]<math>\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}a</math>倍。<ref name="bendwavy, cubohemioctahedron">{{cite klitzing|cho.htm|rooturl=incmats|title=cubohemioctahedron, cho|access-date=2021-09-06|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123042038/https://www.bendwavy.org/klitzing/incmats/cho.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>
=== 定向性 ===
立方半八面體的表面是一個不可[[可定向性|定向]]的曲面<ref name="mathconsult"/>，即無法定義表面上特定點屬於內部或外部，因為任何點都可以在不打洞的情況下經由表面找到一個路徑連接該點對應的背面的位置，這個特性與[[克萊因瓶|克萊因瓶]]類似<ref name="dmccooey,VersiRegular">{{cite web | author = David I. McCooey | url = http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/VersiRegular.html | title = Versi-Regular Polyhedra | publisher = dmccooey.com | access-date = 2021-09-05 | archive-date = 2021-07-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210730090425/http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/VersiRegular.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

