立方半無窮星形八面體是立方半八面體的[[對偶多面體|對偶多面體]]，也是九個對偶半多面體之一<ref>{{Citation | author = {{link-en|馬格努斯·J·溫尼爾|Magnus J. Wenninger|Magnus Wenninger}}    | title=Dual Models | publisher=[[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]] | isbn=978-0-521-54325-5 |mr=730208 | year=1983}} (Page 101, Duals of the (nine) hemipolyhedra)</ref>。其外觀難以與[[八面半無窮星形八面體|八面半無窮星形八面體]]區別。<ref>{{cite mathworld|urlname=Cubohemioctahedron|title=Cubohemioctahedron}}</ref>
